'''''Disquieting Dream''''' is an [[Adventure Mission]] on [[Amphoreus]].

==Steps==
# Wait for Pasithea to appear in the Plaza
# Speak with Pasithea
# Question the nearby citizens
# Question the citizens further away
# Ask the Holy City Guard for clues
# Find a "companion" to help
# Follow Mem's direction and rescue Pasithea
# Speak with Pasithea
# Report the situation to Tribbie
# Go to the Abyss of Fate
# Use the Prophecy Tablet of Oronyx
# Touch the concentrated memory
# Track down the next celestial echo
# Use the Titan's Prophecy Tablet again
# Touch the memory of the past
# Head to the Temple of the Three Fates
# Touch the disorderly memories
# Listen to the whispering in your ears
# Lift the curtain of the past
# Head to the highest level of the temple to witness the end of the maiden's story
# (Optional) Review the law of the judgment
# Continue onwards and search for the priest's remains
# Reach the end of the Temple to receive the Titan's revelation
# Return to Pasithea's side
# Take Pasithea back home
# Touch the final memory

